track_notes: Longer forest trail, so comfortable in summer times. More or less even in the first part until trail crossing Schuhfleck, then steeper on the second part.
track_title: Ascent from car park above Gasthaus Menauer at Grandsberg

track_notes: Drive thru Lindenau, beyond Hotel >Happy Hirsch< till the end of the road. Parking space at the curve, where the gravel road begins. Easy track mostly. Took me about 45min to summit.
Parking place near Berggasthof Menauer, Grandsberg 6, 94374 Schwarzach, Germany
